            "id": 6011389,
            "title": "美中貿易磋商再啟！川普團隊下周赴倫敦與中方會談",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普周五 (6 日) 在 Truth Social 發文宣布，美國財政部長貝森特 (Scott Bessent)、商務部長盧特尼克(Howard Lutnick) 以及美國貿易代表葛里爾 (Jamieson Greer)，將於下周一(9 日) 在倫敦與中國代表舉行會談，討論貿易協議的相關事宜。川普在貼文中表示，預期會議將非常順利，並感謝各界對此事的關注。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011389%2Fl%2Ff90969f63a0c523e63c98afd58570b7f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">美中貿易磋商再啟！川普團隊下周赴倫敦與中方會談(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"圖：川普Truth Social\" data-height=\"280\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"2.1785714285714284\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6011389/m/0079a628dbc5fb3cf6c7199cd8d9ed0f.jpg\" data-width=\"610\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6011389/l/0079a628dbc5fb3cf6c7199cd8d9ed0f.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>圖：川普 Truth Social</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普政府正積極推進與中國的貿易協議談判，此次倫敦會議被視為雙邊經貿談判的關鍵進展。美方代表團由財政部、商務部與貿易代表署的高層官員共同參與，外界關注會議結果是否能進一步化解持續緊張的美中貿易關係。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>持續更新...</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
